00:09:07.219 --> 00:09:09.140
He is Alpha and Omega.

00:09:09.140 --> 00:09:10.539
He's the beginning and the end.

00:09:10.539 --> 00:09:13.859
He is, He was, and He is to come.

00:09:13.859 --> 00:09:16.380
